  "id": "guide/schematics/action",
  "title": "Action",
  "contents": "\n\n\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/schematics/action.md?message=docs%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  </div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n<h1 id=\"action\">Action<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/schematics/action#action\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"overview\">Overview<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/schematics/action#overview\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>Generates an action file that contains an enum of action types,\nan example action class and an exported type union of action classes.</p>\n<h2 id=\"command\">Command<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/schematics/action#command\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<code-example language=\"sh\">\nng generate action ActionName [<a href=\"api/data/RequestData#options\" class=\"code-anchor\">options</a>]\n</code-example>\n<h5 id=\"or\">OR<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/schematics/action#or\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<code-example language=\"sh\">\nng generate a ActionName [<a href=\"api/data/RequestData#options\" class=\"code-anchor\">options</a>]\n</code-example>\n<h3 id=\"options\">Options<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/schematics/action#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p>Provide the project name where the action files will be created.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>--project</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Alias: <code>-p</code></li>\n<li>Type: <code>string</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Use creator functions for actions</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>--creators</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Alias: <code>-c</code></li>\n<li>Type: <code>boolean</code></li>\n<li>Default: <code>true</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nest the actions file within a folder based on the action <code>name</code>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>--flat</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Type: <code>boolean</code></li>\n<li>Default: <code>true</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Group the action file within an <code>actions</code> folder.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>--group</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Alias: <code>-g</code></li>\n<li>Type: <code>boolean</code></li>\n<li>Default: <code>false</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Specifies if api success and failure actions should be generated.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>--api</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Alias: <code>-a</code></li>\n<li>Type: <code>boolean</code></li>\n<li>Default: <code>false</code>  </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Generate a spec file alongside the action file.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>--skipTests</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Type: <code>boolean</code></li>\n<li>Default: <code>false</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"examples\">Examples<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/schematics/action#examples\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>Generate a <code>User</code> actions file with an associated spec file.</p>\n<code-example language=\"sh\">\nng generate action User\n</code-example>\n<p>Generate a <code>User</code> actions file within a nested folder</p>\n<code-example language=\"sh\">\nng generate action User --flat false\n</code-example>\n<p>Generate a <code>User</code> actions file within a nested <code>actions</code> folder</p>\n<code-example language=\"sh\">\nng generate action User --group\n</code-example>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/data/RequestData#options\n - guide/schematics/action#action\n - guide/schematics/action#command\n - guide/schematics/action#examples\n - guide/schematics/action#options\n - guide/schematics/action#or\n - guide/schematics/action#overview\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/schematics/action.md?message=docs%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\n-->"
}